edu.pdx.cs410J.thhoang

Class PhoneCall

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.pdx.cs410J.AbstractPhoneCall
      • edu.pdx.cs410J.thhoang.PhoneCall
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable

    public class PhoneCall
extends AbstractPhoneCall
    This class represents a phone call between a caller (the phone number of the person who originates the call) and callee (the phone number of the person whose receives the phone call). Phone calls begin and end at given times.
    See Also:
